REM Title: Eject (any) mounted disk
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Plays the classic prank but on Macs — pops every ejectable
REM volume. No-op if nothing is mounted.
REM Target: macOS
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING osascript -e 'tell application "Finder" to eject (every disk whose ejectable is true)'
ENTER
